        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../post/8900.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.6 文档 ] 安全系列 —— 登录认证</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-03-09T00:30:47+08:00">2018-03-09</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-03-09T01:07:12+08:00">2018-03-09 01:07:12</time>
