                <a href="../../post/9554.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.7 文档 ] 安全系列 —— 登录认证</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-09-02T10:10:01+08:00">2018-09-02</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-09-05T21:49:06+08:00">2018-09-05 21:49:06</time>
