    <article id="post-7754" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../post/7754.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.5 文档 ] 快速入门 —— 使用 Laragon 在 Windows 中搭建 Laravel 开发环境</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-14T21:58:32+08:00">2017-09-14</time>
