    <article id="post-9529" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../post/9529.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.7 文档 ] 快速入门 —— 目录结构</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-08-28T12:20:31+08:00">2018-08-28</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-09-05T21:47:45+08:00">2018-09-05 21:47:45</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    3427 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../post/9529.html#comments">
                        0 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../post/9529.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08737b9546c5b814704af0b44c66fe9d-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../post/9529.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08737b9546c5b814704af0b44c66fe9d-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>简介
Laravel 默认的目录结构试图为不管是大型应用还是小型应用提供一个良好的起点。当然，你也可以按照自己的喜好重新组织应用的目录结构，因为 Laravel 对于指定类在何处被加载没有任何限制 —— 只要 Composer 可以自动载入它们即可。
Models 目录在哪里？
许多初学者都会困惑 Laravel 为什么没有提供 models 目录，我可以负责任的告诉大家，这是故意的。因...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
