    <article id="post-9525" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../post/9525.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.7 文档 ] 序言 —— 新版特性</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-08-27T00:58:20+08:00">2018-08-27</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-09-02T23:39:22+08:00">2018-09-02 23:39:22</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    8030 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../post/9525.html#comments">
                        7 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../post/9525.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/61c704e68397577f570414836b00ef4d-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../post/9525.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/61c704e68397577f570414836b00ef4d-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>Laravel 5.7 在 Laravel 5.6 的基础上继续进行优化，包括引入 Laravel Nova，认证脚手架中可选的邮箱验证，支持针对未登录用户的授权，集成 Symfony dump-server，本地化通知，以及多个 bug 修复和可用性的提升。
Laravel Nova
Laravel Nova 是一个专门为 Laravel 应用打造的、美观的、一流的后台管理面板，当然，...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
